title: Ashley Bell - Dean Koontz
description:
The girl who said no to death. Bibi Blair is a fierce, funny, dauntless young woman

 whose doctor says she has one year to live. She replies, “We’ll see.” Her sudden

 recovery astonishes medical science.An enigmatic woman convinces Bibi that she

 escaped death so that she can save someone else. Someone named Ashley Bell. But save

 her from what, from whom? And who is Ashley Bell? Where is she? Bibi’s obsession

 with finding Ashley sends her on the run from threats both mystical and worldly,

 including a rich and charismatic cult leader with terrifying ambitions.




 Length: 17:33:48
